path.data-intro: The Green Lines show the path from "EGO" to the selected node.
The Purple Lines show the path from "EGO" to the Jiliwiri inversion of the selected node.

g.data-intro: Hello! This node is "EGO," or the reference point of all kinship relations.

rect.data-intro: Clicking on "EGO" will unhighlight the pathways.

circle.data-intro: Click on a node to use the program. The node and two lines will be highlighted.
